title: Marshall Faulk Stops By To Preview Super Bowl LVI
description:
Jalen & Jacoby are joined by Rams legend and Hall of Famer Marshall Faulk to talk all things Super Bowl LVI. Plus the guys discuss Kyler Murray scrubbing all Cardinals-related content from his social media accounts, what’s next for Tom Brady, Devin Booker’s monster performance against Bulls, pressure on Julius Randle and Knicks and much more.
